data.name: lboHelpText.Text
data.value:
INSERT
Upload to the database the information of new material with a registration number.
UPDATE
Add or change the information of an existing material in the database.
SEARCH
Search and extract to report file information from the database.
REPORT ANALYZER
Analyze one or more extracted report files.

data.name: cbSearchDocType.Tag
data.value: (CASE WHEN document_type_enumeration = '0' THEN 'Signal from DMOS' WHEN document_type_enumeration = '1' THEN 'Decree(from investigation officer)' WHEN document_type_enumeration = '2' THEN 'Decree (from prosecutor)' WHEN document_type_enumeration = '3' THEN 'Request from DMOS' ELSE 'Police Check' END) AS 'Type'
